</td>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:31%; padding:0in 0in 0in 0in; height:30px; background-color:#d9d9d9; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top">
<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="vertical-align:baseline"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Positive for radiculopathy if pt experiences radiating pain to the leg being lifted </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
