<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="vertical-align:baseline"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Slump Test </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:20%; padding:0in 0in 0in 0in; height:40px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top">
<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="vertical-align:baseline"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Lumbosacral nerve roots </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
