<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="vertical-align:baseline"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">if any of the steps reproduces radicular pain <br/>
			 Use with straight leg raise  </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
